========================
EFL Physics Engine v 0.1
========================

Prerequisites
-------------
Evas - for lists and the demo app
Ecore - for timers

Inspiration
-----------
Akamaru (http://people.freedesktop.org/~krh/akamaru.git/)
Advance Character Physics, Thomas Jakobsen. (http://www.teknikus.dk/tj/gdc2001.htm)

Installation
------------
./bootstrap # only needed if from git/cvs/etc
./configure
make
#make install 

(for now, run the demo from the src/bin dir. it won't work when installed due to an image path being hard coded)
